metadata.name: The King of Venice -  dyptyck
metadata.description:
Gypsy king with silver charm,
Fingers trace the lines of fate.

In Luna's light, Venus' sway,
Destiny's hand, The stars align, 
on Midas' palm, A mystic myth, 
with gifts so calm.

Sacred ring, his gift, his fame.
The whispering spirit lives on, 
In name.
